@{B} B U G S @{UB}
__________________________________________________________________________
@{FG SHINE}ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ@{FG TEXT}

@{B} KNOWN BUGS @{UB}
@{B}------------@{UB}

  · GuideML crashes if an AmigaGuide node name is longer than 100 chars.
  · GuideML might fail if a line is longer than 1000 chars.
  · GuideML might crash if a mangled AmigaGuide file is feeded.
  · No stack checkings. Ensure a stack of at least 4096 bytes.
  · There is no built-in image for HELP or RETRACE buttons.

Some of them are plain lazyness. Please excuse!


@{B} KNOWN ENFORCER/MUNGWALL/PATCHWORK HITS @{UB}
@{B}----------------------------------------@{UB}

  · none yet...  :-)

